Outside Partnership

Landscape architecture committed to revitalizing Detroit and enhancing our quality of life. We offer design and project management services for government agencies, land conservancies and non-profits. Our strengths include design and management of complex, fast-track projects that require interdisciplinary cooperation and consensus building.
